cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use JuMinuit.jl in a publication, please cite both this software and
  the upstream Minuit algorithms (James & Roos 1975) that it ports.
title: "JuMinuit.jl: a native-Julia port of Minuit2"
abstract: >-
  Native-Julia port of the C++ Minuit2 function-minimization library — a
  drop-in replacement for IMinuit.jl, with an iminuit-style API and
  error-analysis tools beyond HESSE/MINOS (Monte-Carlo Δχ² regions, bootstrap,
  jackknife, multi-modal solution detection).
type: software
authors:
